sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Operator as "Codex validation"
    participant Local as "BlogAI.Web local host"
    participant Deployed as "https://api.global-webnet.com"
    participant WebDeploy as "WebDeploy profile apiglobalwebnet"

    Operator->>Local: GET /
    Local-->>Operator: 200, guardrail rendered
    Operator->>Local: GET /local-dev
    Local-->>Operator: 200, guardrail rendered, diagnostic-only/not-production-auth text

    Operator->>Deployed: GET /
    Deployed-->>Operator: 200, guardrail missing
    Operator->>Deployed: GET /local-dev
    Deployed-->>Operator: 200, guardrail missing

    Operator->>WebDeploy: dotnet publish with profile
    WebDeploy-->>Operator: 401 Unauthorized, no update applied

    Operator->>WebDeploy: dotnet publish with profile and explicit env-sourced credential
    WebDeploy-->>Operator: Publish Succeeded

    Operator->>Deployed: GET /
    Deployed-->>Operator: 200, guardrail rendered
    Operator->>Deployed: GET /local-dev
    Deployed-->>Operator: 200, guardrail rendered
